Crosstable TUI
==============

Simple ncurses program for managing round robin tournaments.

Compile
=======

Install ncursesw via your package manager.

$ cd src
$ g++ -o crosstable-tui -I. -lncursesw *.cpp
$ ./crosstable-tui

